00:09:00,418 --> 00:09:02,018
We'll put a little snow on this mountain.

242
00:09:02,778 --> 00:09:03,817
Little bit of snow.

243
00:09:03,817 --> 00:09:04,997
Pull it out very flat.

244
00:09:04,998 --> 00:09:06,598
Very, very flat.

245
00:09:06,597 --> 00:09:07,916
Just like we did before.

246
00:09:07,917 --> 00:09:09,758
And then cut across it.

