00:09:24,570 --> 00:09:28,090
No pressure. Absolutely no pressure.

254
00:09:30,350 --> 00:09:31,918
No pressure.

255
00:09:33,828 --> 00:09:35,489
All that's touching the canvas is that

256
00:09:35,490 --> 00:09:37,149
little roll of paint that's on the knife.

257
00:09:38,239 --> 00:09:39,590
And then you begin thinking about

258
00:09:39,590 --> 00:09:41,469
where the light would strike as it

259
00:09:41,469 --> 00:09:43,621
just comes through here.

260
00:09:43,789 --> 00:09:45,068
Now, some people find it easier

261
00:09:45,068 --> 00:09:46,549
